---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div>
    <h3 class="wwg-main-title">
        <Icon name="mdi:wordpress" class="wwg-wp-icon" />
        ¿Usas WordPress? Guía de Instalación
    </h3>

    <div class="wwg-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="wwg-option">
            <div class="wwg-option-header">
                <strong class="wwg-option-title">Inserción de iFrame</strong>
            </div>
            <p class="wwg-text">Añade un bloque de <strong>HTML personalizado</strong> en tu editor de WordPress y pega el código iFrame. Para que la altura se ajuste automáticamente sin cortarse, puedes instalar el plugin gratuito <strong>Iframely</strong> o configurar una altura fija CSS en el bloque.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .wwg-main-title {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--wi-education-title-color);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .wwg-wp-icon {
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        color: #21759b;
    }

    .wwg-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        background-color: var(--wi-wp-guide-bg);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--wi-wp-guide-border);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wwg-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
    }

    .wwg-option > * + * {
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .wwg-option-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .wwg-badge {
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 12px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wwg-badge--a {
        background-color: var(--wi-wp-badge-a-bg);
        color: inherit;
    }

    .wwg-badge--b {
        background-color: var(--wi-wp-badge-b-bg);
        color: var(--wi-wp-badge-b-color);
    }

    .wwg-option-title {
        display: block;
        color: var(--wi-wp-option-title-color);
    }

    .wwg-text {
        color: var(--wi-wp-text-color);
        line-height: 1.625;
    }

    .wwg-alert {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.625;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .wwg-alert--amber {
        background-color: var(--wi-wp-alert-amber-bg);
        color: var(--wi-wp-alert-amber-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--wi-wp-alert-amber-border);
    }

    .wwg-alert--green {
        background-color: var(--wi-wp-alert-green-bg);
        color: var(--wi-wp-alert-green-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--wi-wp-alert-green-border);
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .wwg-alert-icon {
        width: 1.25rem;
        height: 1.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wwg-alert-icon--emerald {
        color: var(--wi-wp-alert-icon-emerald);
    }

    .wwg-steps {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .wwg-steps > * + * {
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }

    .wwg-step {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--wi-wp-step-color);
    }

    .wwg-step-icon {
        width: 1.25rem;
        height: 1.25rem;
        color: #cbd5e1;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
</style>
